  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  All adult, English-speaking patients in the practice of Dr. Jesse Jupiter, Dr.
             Chaitanya Mudgal, or Dr. David Ring electing splint treatment for mallet deformity
             will be invited to enroll on their follow-up visit 6-8 weeks after initiating splint
             treatment.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Open lesions

          2. Mallet fracture more than 2 weeks old

          3. Mallet fracture with subluxation of the distal interphalangeal joint.
      </textblock>
